1 AN ACT relating to agriculture.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 246.040 is amended to read as follows:
4 (1) The Commissioner shall be the head of the department. He or she shall keep his or
5 her office at the seat of government and devote his or her entire time to the duties
6 of his or her office.
7 (2) The Commissioner may employ necessary personnel to assist in carrying out his or
8 her duties.
